dspkg-validator
------------------------------------------
Validator for Synthrt package

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libdspkg-validator-devel-0.0.1+git20250904-1bl1
  libdspkg-validator0-0.0.1+git20250904-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  nlohmann_json-3.12.0-1bl2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/wolfgitpr/dspkg-validator

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/wolfgitpr/dspkg-validator.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack dspkg-validator-0.0.1+git20250904-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./dspkg-validator-0.0.1+git20250904-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/dspkg-validator-0.0.1+git20250904-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/dspkg-validator-0.0.1+git20250904-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdspkg-validator0-0.0.1+git20250904-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdspkg-validator-devel-0.0.1+git20250904-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

